Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnShunpu}yeeeart！yeeeart！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.09,忍者杀手,,0,0,0,,{\fnShunpu}yeeeart！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnShunpu}aaaargh！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnShunpu}yeeeart！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶！{\fnShunpu}yeeeart！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好了！把他让给我 让老子我亲自和他玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,姆哈哈哈哈...你好 忍者杀手·桑 老子我是老元·宽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,敢对抗老子我这事 先要夸夸你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:13.24,忍者杀手,,0,0,0,,{\fnShunpu}yeeeart！！！！！！！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,欲速...则不达！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,斩草除根基金社 CEO 老元·宽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnShunpu}aaaargh！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不能拘泥于眼前小事 必须要怀有广阔的视野 忍者杀手·桑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来 忍者杀手·桑
