Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnShunpu}yeeeart！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.49,忍者杀手,,0,0,0,,{\fnShunpu}yeeeart！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnShunpu}yeeeart！
